contentrichtext.text: '''RAA''' or '''Raa''' may refer to several things: ==RAA== * [[Ralph Appelbaum Associates]] * Rational Asset Analyzer, a software analysis tool from the [[Rational Software]] division of [[IBM]]. * [[Recreation and Amusement Association]], a system of brothels set up by the Japanese government for US occupation forces * [[Recreational Aircraft Association]] * [[Recreational Aviation Australia]] * [[Reductio ad absurdum]] * [[Reeve Aleutian Airways]] * [[Regional Airline Association]] (USA) * [[Renin-Angiotensin-Aldosterone system]] * [[Requiem: Avenging Angel]], a 1999 [[first-person shooter]] video game * [[Research on Armenian Architecture]] * [[Research & Academic Architecture, PC]] * ''Riksantikvarie채mbetet'' ([[Swedish National Heritage Board|National Heritage Board]] of Sweden) * [[Right atrial appendage]] *''Rise Against Alliansen'' (Swedish supporters of the band [[Rise Against]]) * [[Royal Australian Artillery]], a corps in the Australian Army * [[Royal Automobile Association]] * [[Ruby Application Archive]] * [[The Rural Alberta Advantage]], a Canadian indie band ==Raa== * [[Tama-nui-te-r훮|Raa or R훮]], the personification of the sun in M훮ori mythology * [[Raa Atoll]], an administrative division of the Maldives * [[Thaana|Raa]], the fourth consonant of the Thaana abugaida used in Dhivehi * [[Raa (film)|Raa]], an [[Upendra]] film Released in 2001 {{disambig}}
